w place. Along with this, the app has a ratings and review option to help the users with the ground zero facts about that particular property or listing.</p>', 'Find Your Commercial Rentals with a Sophisticated Mobile App', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'find-your-commercial-rentals-with-a-sophisticated-mobile-app__trashed', '', '', '2020-05-13 00:16:19', '2020-05-13 00:16:19', '', 0, 'https://www.dectar.com/blog/?p=6098', 0, 'post', '', 0),
